VVC Race Timer script  v1.6
by SDragon

Commands:
    init
        Reads the connected ship name and gets the race ready to go.

    start
        Starts the race.

    stop
        Finishes the race.

    checkpoint
        Records the checkpoint name and time.

    reset
        Resets the script.

    clear-standings
        Clears all race standing information.

    remove-standing
        Remove a ship name from the race standings.
        Usage:
            remove-standing Ship Name here
